name: Metallic Ball
description: This generative artwork is made by Bohdan Svyrydov. The metallic ball shrank before our eyes. However, the process proceeded as quickly as it had begun, and nothing could stop it. The ball shrank until it turned into a black dot, and then suddenly burst into a dazzling white light. Now the air was filled with an iridescent suspension, as if the whole world around had turned into liquid glass, and then everything disappeared. Find more about the artists here - http://linktr.ee/bohdansvyrydov
